name: OnlineCheck
0:
”Alexa, start online check”
”Alexa, open Online Check”
”Alexa, ask Online Check for help”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: online check
des: Of course, simply asking "Alexa, are you there?" is enough to check if your internet connection is working. But it's more fun this way: if you're online, this skill will play the typical sounds you hear when you dial up to the internet with an analog modem.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
